Package domainlayer

Class DocumentKeeper

java.lang.Object
domainlayer.DocumentKeeper
public class DocumentKeeper
extends java.lang.Object
A class that keeps track of the documents associated to the windows in the UI-layer, as well as the ContentFrame that currently has focus.

  • Constructor Summary

    Constructors
    Constructor Description
    DocumentKeeper()
    Initialise this DocumentKeeper with an empty hashmap that maps the UI-layer objects to documents.
